Fisher & Paykel Lady Zest™ Q Nasal CPAP Mask and Headgear,4004XX,configurable,1,Mask & Headgear,Fisher & Paykel,

Features

  • Offers a lighter and easy to use design
  • FlexiFit Technology - Automatically adjusts to a wide range of nasal and facial contours.
  • Uniquely quiet
  • Latex Free CPAP mask
  • Glider Strap - Provides freedom of movement while maintaining a seal.
  • Easy-Clip Silicone Seal - Allows one-step connection or removal for quick and effortless cleaning.
  • Advanced Bias Air Diffuser - Disperses the airflow away from the sleeper’s partner, and minimizes exhaust flow noise.
  • Improved Stretchgear 4 point CPAP Headgear - A comfortable and breathable elastic headgear.
  • Hidden Strap Release - Easy one-step removal of headgear.
The exclusive design of the Fisher & Paykel Lady Zest™ Q CPAP Mask has that feminine touches every female user yearns for. Nothing has been lost in translation since just like the original Fisher & Paykel Zest CPAP mask , the Lady Zest Q CPAP mask provides a lightweight feel and optimal fit. And just like the original patients will still enjoy the easy to use configuration as well as the peace and quiet. The noise reduction is due to the Air Diffuser integrated into the elbow assembly of the mask.

    • Easy-Clip Silicone Seal with VTS™

  • FlexFoam™ CPAP Cushion


    • FlexiFit™ Technology

  • Glider™ Strap


    • Stretchgear™ CPAP Headgear

• The headgear for the Opus provides a reinforced support structure and thin design making it ideal for side sleeping.
• Anatomically designed nasal pillows provide an excellent seal and added comfort.
• Advanced Short Hose System can be mounted either in front or on the side of the face, or you have the option to not anchor the hose.
• The Opus features an advanced bias air diffuser system that makes the mask exceptionally quiet.
• Soft-Lip Nasal Cushion - Silicone seal provides even more support and comfort, by conforming naturally to the upper lip.
• 360-Swivel - The unique ball-in-joint combination allows the tubing to freely move.

column2:
Paykel Opus 360 CPAP Nasal Pillows and Headgear provides an unprecedented level of comfort through the uniquely designed nasal pillows system and headgear combination. The anatomically shaped nasal pillows of this CPAP nasal interface have been refined to offer greater mobility and flexibility. The frame and headgear have also been revised to provide a better side-sleeping experience, as well as a facially contoured design for a more comfortable fit.

The Nasal Interface System and headgear come fully assembled, with 3 nasal pillows included (Small, Medium, and Large) for patient convenience, ease of use and a correct fit the first time. This nasal pillows interface can be used with any CPAP machine or BiPAP therapy. Replacement parts available for extended life of this CPAP nasal interface.

column1:
Features

  • FlexiFit Technology with Auto-contouring design includes the new FlexiFoam cushion.
  • FlexiFoam Active-Contouring Cushion - Greater comfort using a soft, lightweight and supportive foam.
  • Unique Glider Strap.
  • Easy Release Headgear Cord for one-step removal.
  • Under-the-Chin Cushion Design.
  • Crown Strap with the 4 point headgear provides additional support.

• New padded T shaped forehead support - provides added stability and comfort.
  • Advanced Bias Air Diffuser.

column2: Paykel Forma Full Face CPAP Mask is the third generation of Full Faced masks. It forms a superior seal and provides even more comfort with a greater range of movement through the active contouring of the new FlexiFoam Cushion. A new padded T shaped forehead support adds stability to the mask base, and works in harmony with the highly contoured Silicone Seal and Under-the-Chin design to enhance your sleep performance. With its ease of use, superior conforming silicone seal, and the FlexiFoam cushion, the new Forma Full Face CPAP mask sets a new standard.

Paykel Forma mask offers an improved seal and a more comfortable fit due to the interaction between the new and improved FlexiFoam cushion and the patented Under-Chin Design (as seen in the FlexiFit 431 and FlexiFit 432). The Forma Full Face CPAP mask comes fully assembled and ready for use out of the box. Easy to clean, easy to use, with replacement parts available.

column2: Paykel FlexiFit 432 can be used with any manufactures CPAP or BiPAP machines.
